title: Godspeed You! Black Emperor - All Lights Fucked on the Hairy Amp
description:
This is just two songs of the infamous album, "All Lights Fucked on the Hairy Amp Drooling." Now, of course, it is rumored that this may not even exist, but that is not what one man said posting on Reddit. He posted a link to a WAV file that I, and many others, downloaded to hear. It sounds like it could be it, but I decided why not cut it, convert it, and post it here on TPB. I know it is ALAC, and many prefer FLAC, but I'm lazy. This does not belong to a specific label and GY!BE allows the free trade of their music so it should be legal.
